{"tid":2232603,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"貓貓下爬無啦啦損咗一噠","createTime":"2020-10-06T13:19:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T12:55:02.000Z","uid":368051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b9c574f8940c13314b42c9beb2af7e927a16ad2a","tid":2232603,"uid":368051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T13:19:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EzVJH51.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEzVJH51.png&h=2a9f1055&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如題<br />\n摸落去個位係少少硬，好似傷口結焦咁<br />\n但係又有少少濕，好似人嘅傷口咁<br />\n比起尋日又大噠咗<br />\n係咪皮膚病<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然佢平時又哀嚎又為食<br />\n不過成日都好得意<br />\n<br />\n附圖幾張<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u3aan84.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu3aan84.jpg&h=f82c8a00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZrFmuO6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZrFmuO6.jpg&h=6cdd7dce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2nRkLnR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2nRkLnR.jpg&h=4f827e63&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7dd18717a75a797b94a9b43c775534af2b7a4bb5","tid":2232603,"uid":293,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T13:21:05.000Z","msg":"寵物健康問題一律答<br />\n去睇獸醫"},{"pid":"27a58e8fc55f3aef7c8a39956a0df0ef4c8bf481","tid":2232603,"uid":85427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T13:21:24.000Z","msg":"睇獸醫啦 慳乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c3ec4440905328b2869450cbc15608fef508c6","tid":2232603,"uid":4394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl